the woman who loved elvis is an american television film that aired on abc on april 18 , 1993 from 9:00 to 11:00 pm eastern time . the film starred roseanne barr , her then husband tom arnold , it also starred cynthia gibb , danielle harris , and sally kirkland . it was filmed in ottumwa , iowa , where arnold was born . based on laura kalpakian 's novel " graced land " .